title: Texas Tech's win streak rises to nine - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Texas Tech's win streak rises to nine - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The No. 19 Texas Tech baseball team defeated Merrimack College, 12-4, on Sunday afternoon at Rip Griffin Park. The win completed a four-game sweep for the Red Raiders, outscoring the visitors from the Boston area 70-12 over the last three days.
